languages.text: "Приветствую тебя, пытливый странник или странница, что смогли найти мое послание и разгадать загадку! Я, Парсимус Девейн, владыка Футфола, первопроходец {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Простора Коронус{/g}, рад гостям моего великолепого дворца меж звезд".

"Greetings to you, keen wanderer who found my message and solved my riddle! I, Parsimus Dewain, master of Footfall, trailblazer of the {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Expanse{/g}, am pleased to welcome visitors to my magnificent palace in the stars."

languages.text: 「鋭い洞察力を持つ放浪者の方よ、ワタシのメッセージを発見し、見事に謎を解いたことを称賛する！ワタシはフットフォールの主であり{g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}エクスパンス{/g}の開拓者、パルシムス・ドウェインと申す。星々の中に眠る我が壮大な宮廷への来客者として温かく迎えよう」

languages.text: “向你致意，敏锐的流浪者！你找到了我留下的信息，解开了我设置的谜题！我，帕西姆斯·德维恩，落脚港的主人，{g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}科罗努斯扩区{/g}的先驱者，欢迎所有访客参观我宏伟的星际宫殿。”
languages.original_text: "Greetings to you, keen wanderer who found my message and solved my riddle! I, Parsimus Dewain, master of Footfall, trailblazer of the {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Expanse{/g}, am pleased to welcome visitors to my magnificent palace in the stars."

languages.text: «¡Saludos, trotamundos de mente aguda que ha encontrado mi mensaje y resuelto mi acertijo! Yo, Parsimus Dewain, creador de Paso y pionero de la {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Extensión{/g}, estoy orgulloso de poder recibir visitas en mi magnífico palacio estelar».
languages.original_text: "Greetings to you, keen wanderer who found my message and solved my riddle! I, Parsimus Dewain, master of Footfall, trailblazer of the {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Expanse{/g}, am pleased to welcome visitors to my magnificent palace in the stars."

languages.text: « Salutations, vous qui avez trouvé mon message et résolu mon énigme ! Je me présente : Parsimus Dewain, maître de Castel et pionnier des {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Étendues{/g}. Je suis ravi d'accueillir des visiteurs dans mon magnifique palais au milieu des étoiles. »

languages.text: "Ich grüße Euch, {mf|kühner Wanderer, der|kühne Wanderin, die} Ihr meine Nachricht gefunden und mein Rätsel gelöst habt! Ich, Parsimus Dewain, Herr von Footfall, Wegbereiter der {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Ausdehnung{/g}, heiße alle Besucher meines prächtigen Palasts in den Sternen willkommen."

languages.text: "Mesajımı bulup bilmecemi çözen keskin zekâlı gezginlere selam olsun! Bendeniz Binliman'ın efendisi, {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Enginlik'in{/g} öncüsü Parsimus Dewain. Misafirleri yıldızların içindeki muazzam sarayıma kabul etmekten mutluluk duyuyorum."

traits.locale_text: "Mesajımı bulan ve bilmecemi çözen keskin zekâlı gezgine selam olsun! Ben, Parsimus Dewain, Binliman'ın efendisi, {g|Encyclopedia:KoronusExpanse}Enginlik{/g}'in öncüsü, ziyaretçileri yıldızların içindeki muazzam sarayıma kabul etmekten mutluluk duyuyorum."
